<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Abyride Service Contract - Welcome</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
          font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
          background: linear-gradient(135deg,#293751 0%, #47B2E4  100%);
          min-height: 100vh;
          padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
          max-width: 900px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          background: white;
          border-radius: 20px;
          box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
          overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
       background: linear-gradient(135deg,#293751 0%, #47B2E4  100%);
          color: #293751;
          padding: 40px 30px;
          text-align: center;
          position: relative;
        }
        .header::before {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          top: -50%; left: -50%;
          width: 200%; height: 200%;
          background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
          animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
          0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
          50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
        }
        .header h1 {
          font-size: 2.3rem;
          font-weight: 700;
          position: relative;
          z-index: 1;
        }
        .header img {
          max-width:200px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
          height:100px;
        }
        .content { padding: 30px; }
        h2 {
          color: #293751;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
          font-size: 1.8rem;
        }
        h3 {
          color: #293751;
          margin: 25px 0 15px;
          font-size: 1.4rem;
        }
        p {
          line-height: 1.6;
          margin-bottom: 15px;
          color: #333;
        }
        .status-badge {
          background: #E3F2FD;
          color: #293751;
          padding: 8px 16px;
          border-radius: 25px;
          font-weight: 600;
          display: inline-block;
          margin: 15px 0;
          border: 1px solid #BBDEFB;
        }
        .contract-details-grid, .info-grid {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
          gap: 15px;
          margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-card, .info-item {
          background: #F5FAFF;
          border: 1px solid #E1F5FE;
          padding: 20px;
          border-radius: 12px;
        }
        .detail-card strong, .info-item strong {
          display: block;
          color: #293751;
          font-weight: 600;
          margin-bottom: 8px;
          font-size: 0.9rem;
          text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .detail-card span, .info-item span {
          color: #47B2E4;
          font-size: 1rem;
          font-weight: 500;
        }
        .signature-note {
          background: #E1F5FE;
          border-left: 5px solid #47B2E4;
          padding: 20px;
          margin-top: 30px;
          border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
          background: #F5FAFF;
          text-align: center;
          padding: 30px;
          margin-top: 30px;
          border-top: 1px solid #E1F5FE;
        }
        .footer h3 {
          color: #293751;
          margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .footer a {
          color: #47B2E4;
          text-decoration: none;
          font-weight: 500;
        }
        .footer p {
          color: #666;
          font-size: 0.95rem;
          margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .section-title {
          position: relative;
          padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .section-title::after {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          bottom: 0;
          left: 0;
          width: 50px;
          height: 3px;
          background: #47B2E4;
          border-radius: 3px;
        }
        .account-access {
       background: linear-gradient(135deg,#293751 0%, #47B2E4  100%);
          padding: 25px;
          border-radius: 12px;
          margin: 30px 0;
          text-align: center;
        }
        .account-access h3 {
          color: white;
          margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
           .account-access p {
          color: white;
          margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .account-access .btn {
          display: inline-block;
          background: #47B2E4;
          color: white;
          padding: 12px 25px;
          border-radius: 30px;
          text-decoration: none;
          font-weight: 600;
          margin-top: 15px;
          transition: all 0.3s ease;
          box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(71, 178, 228, 0.3);
        }
        .account-access .btn:hover {
          background: #3A9DCC;
          transform: translateY(-2px);
          box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(71, 178, 228, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
      <img src="https://aspirebridgerwanda.org/abyride-logo.png" alt="Abyride Logo" />
      <h1>ðŸš— Abyride Application Received</h1>
      <p>Thank you for applying to join our platform</p>
    </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-section">
                <h2>Contract Confirmation</h2>
                <p>Dear <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>
                <p>We're excited to welcome you to the Abyride family! Your service contract has been successfully created and is now active.</p>
                <p>Below you'll find all the important details about your contract and our services.</p>
                <span class="status-badge status-active">Contract Active</span>
            </div>

            <div class="client-section">
                <h3 class="section-title">ðŸ‘¤ Driver Information</h3>
                <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <strong>Full Name</strong>
                        <span>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <strong>Date of Birth</strong>
                        <span>{{dateOfBirth}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <strong>Gender</strong>
                        <span>{{gender}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <strong>Nationality</strong>
                        <span>{{nationality}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <strong>Phone Number</strong>
                        <span>{{phoneNumber}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <strong>Email Address</strong>
                        <span>{{email}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="account-access">
                <h3>More Details Available in Your Account</h3>
                <p>For complete contract details, payment information, and service management, please log in to your Abyride driver account.</p>
                <a href="https://abyride.com/AbyrideDriver" class="btn">Login to Your Account</a>
            </div>

            <div class="signature-note">
                <p>ðŸ“„ This email serves as your official digital contract confirmation. Please keep this for your records and reference.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <h3>Need Assistance?</h3>
            <p>Our support team is available 24/7 to help with any questions</p>
            <p><a href="mailto:support@abyride.com">support@abyride.com</a> | <a href="tel:+1234567890">+1 (234) 567-890</a></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9;">
                Thank you for choosing Abyride LLC - Your trusted transportation partner<br>
                <em>Excellence in Motion, Service in Every Mile</em>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>